snippet.title: Wuthering Waves · Dev Talk · Prelude EP. 2 - Combat System
snippet.description:
Dear Rovers,

Many of you may be eager to find out how combat is presented within the game.
In "Wuthering Waves · Dev Talk · Prelude" - EP. 2, we will be taking a closer look at the Combat System, from Basic Controls to its Core Mechanics.

Heed the Prelude. 

Pre sign-up for the game:
https://wutheringwaves.kurogame.com/en

♦ Check out our other official links
Official Website: https://wutheringwaves.kurogame.com/en
Official Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Wuthering-Waves-108346541748778
Official Discord: https://discord.gg/wutheringwaves 
Official Twitter: https://twitter.com/Wuthering_Waves
Official Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/WutheringWaves

#WutheringWaves
